Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:36.49,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Chains of a Warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:39.71,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.71,0:01:45.25,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before the Jirocho gang and Lady Kada control the Kabuki district.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.00,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.35,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,You're merely using me to help your father take over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:53.76,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I could say the same about you, Lady Kada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:02:00.38,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the collar around my old man's neck has been released.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:04.07,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,That old hag took away the flowers and freedom my father once had.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:05.51,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that my old man will now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:08.27,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Pay more attention to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:14.28,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that you're the one who can breathe easy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:18.56,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,You must be overjoyed to know that the woman who stole your father from you is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:21.82,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is why I hate women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.08,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,They're always so suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:28.14,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll need you to take care of Saigo's kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:32.17,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows when that sheman will betray us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.08,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Pirako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:38.12,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,Jirocho doesn't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:41.14,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,You can eliminate every obstacle in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.65,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,You can spend your entire life serving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:44.52,Main01,Kada,0000,0000,0000,,He will never turn to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.34,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:48.23,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Could you cut it out, Lady Kada?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:54.35,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't shut your mouth, I'll have to make some flowers, you hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.95,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Greater Edo Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:10.38,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Catherine, you should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.64,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,You have been standing there for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.98,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I do not require any rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:17.05,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I take your place, Madame Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.08,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura-chan, shouldn't you get some rest too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.73,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not skanky enough to go to sleep in someone else's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.13,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.81,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,What if I wake up to find out she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:29.92,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:31.33,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:33.49,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You should go home and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.19,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,She would be upset if she learned that everyone was ruining their health.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:40.16,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,You have no home to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:43.24,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place for you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.38,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Saigo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.12,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,That fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.41,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,I kept telling her to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.97,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Saigo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:52.05,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Was that phone call...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:55.73,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.48,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:59.47,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nothing I can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.44,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,The day after tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:07.89,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs Gin-chan\NSnack Otose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:07.57,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Your place will be destroyed by the Four Devas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.64,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,The day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:14.05,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,You have until then to pack up and leave this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.23,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.87,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:20.87,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place for you here in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:25.22,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,The entire Kabuki district is against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.28,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Did they take your kid hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.78,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.42,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,They appear to be testing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:37.12,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I'll do anything to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:38.49,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Saigo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:42.06,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Pako, can you take care of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.76,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.34,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm closing up shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:48.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.10,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.80,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san was left for dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.37,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Her bar was destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.61,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,And you're just gonna turn tail and run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even take Jirocho one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.97,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,When did you become so pathetic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.86,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Sakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.46,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna leave, you can leave by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:09.78,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,I won't! I won't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why Gran went by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,To protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you still insist on dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,you're free to stay behind and get yourself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:23.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs and Gran's bar are being closed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:25.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're just strangers now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Free to do as we please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:30.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be doing just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:30.78,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:32.00,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:38.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt I can protect anything now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.32,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:43.95,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gintoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.78,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kabuki District 1st Street
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:51.31,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it feel like there aren't many people around these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.87,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.25,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,There's a war brewing around these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.04,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,A war?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.97,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,The factional rivalry between the Four Devas is heating up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.38,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's too scared to come near this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.39,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:06.32,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We've managed to survive everything that's come before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.17,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:10.43,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Puppet House
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:10.43,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,But there are rumors that Otose's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.42,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.57,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,She got in a fight with Jirocho's gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:17.18,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,And it sounds like Katsuo, one of their young leaders, also died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:22.39,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,But there's this rookie who's filling in for Katsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:26.69,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she persuaded Kada and Saigo to help crush Otose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:31.01,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,I still owe her for lending me money when I was in debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:34.33,Main01,G,0000,0000,0000,,I owe her for helping me out when I got in a fight with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:37.56,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go protect Otose-san's bar then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.21,Main01,H,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. I'd be throwing my life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:45.00,Main01,I,0000,0000,0000,,In this town, the wicked live longer than the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.70,Main01,J,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows when the three remaining Devas will turn on one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:51.34,Main01,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably time to get out of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:58.85,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs Gin-chan\NSnack Otose
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:59.37,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,The Kabuki District, a town which accepts the clean and unclean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:05.35,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,I was unable to predict that we would be chased out of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:10.43,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Otose loved this town of good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.76,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,But now, we can never...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:17.92,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,Why must we abandon Otose's bar? Our bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.12,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:26.02,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,If we die, Otose-san will have risked her life for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:30.10,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Otose-san will be moved out of the Kabuki district hospital tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.14,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to visit her every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:36.60,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll have to stay away from the Kabuki district.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:40.39,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're alive, we can always start...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.52,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Start over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.94,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,S-Start...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.89,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.01,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.73,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:16.18,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So you couldn't take on the Four Devas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:21.82,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think our boss would actually attack Otose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:27.08,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You probably thought you could calm things down by saving my life, but tough luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:29.20,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.21,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.75,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying to save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.09,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I just needed you to spill your guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get those guts out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.06,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What do you wanna know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:46.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you surprised that Jirocho attacked Gran?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.46,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.82,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The boss and Otose have known each other since they were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.68,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You could say they were childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.88,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The boss was a pretty naughty kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:02.15,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but Otose was there to straighten him out every time he tried something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:05.52,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Even after he got into organized crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:10.32,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Otose was the only one who stood by him and tried to straighten him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:17.14,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the boss became a vigilante who was popular enough to be considered a leader of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:21.36,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Jirocho, man among men, would never have existed without Otose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.98,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, nobody could defeat the boss in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:30.47,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But, there was one man who managed to triumph over the boss once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:35.08,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsugoro Terada, a cop who was also a leader of the town
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.95,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,and Otose's husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:41.55,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,A man who was strong in a fight and stuck to his ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:44.26,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone had to love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:46.69,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Cop and vigilante.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.62,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,They got in a fight once because of their different positions,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.56,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,but they both fought to protect their town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:56.50,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't long before they became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.29,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But there was one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:03.53,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,They were in love with the same woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:10.04,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,The boss backed down because he wanted Otose to be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:13.80,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,since he figured a vigilante wouldn't be able to provide that happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:19.05,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But Tatsugoro got himself killed, which left Otose alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.18,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,And he died in the middle of a battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.66,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,taking a bullet that was meant for the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:30.44,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,900)}Doromizu Gang
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:33.07,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,When the boss returned from the war, his wife and daughter were waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:37.67,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But the boss paid no attention to his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:42.16,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,He was willing to do anything, no matter how underhanded it was, for the sake of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:48.96,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he didn't have the right to be a father or a vigilante.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:54.92,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it, what was it, that drove the boss to give up all he had to stay in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:59.77,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he's struck down the old lady, I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.80,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That said, I'm one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.33,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for the boss who took me in, or his daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.42,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to have a hole in my gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:11.92,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,That's my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:16.72,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,But was this really the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.98,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,Will this really make them happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:25.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They're never gonna be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,...'cause I'm gonna crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:29.76,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,So you were putting on a show for the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:31.50,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't stand a chance by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:35.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back on my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.63,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Joe Schmo, take care of Gran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.80,Main01,Katsuo,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You always return the favor, seven for three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:49.64,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you stay here to watch this old woman pass on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:51.70,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,Gintoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:55.55,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:57.66,Main01,Otose,0000,0000,0000,,...you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:04.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Gran, I promise to pay off the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.19,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.49,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,How did it feel to cut down the woman you loved?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:21.15,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,How did it feel to manipulate a bunch of old men and women?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:23.24,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:26.55,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I did it all for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:30.98,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Next, you'll have Saigo destroy Otose's bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.12,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:35.81,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Did that vixen put you up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.27,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:40.32,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,This is part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:44.66,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,There are many people left in this town who were involved with Otose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:47.69,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use this chance to flush them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.48,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Saigo happens to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:52.77,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,Will it really work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:13:00.21,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't need to worry. The old woman's buddies aren't in this town anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.21,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,The watchdog's chains have been snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:08.67,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to keep your promise to not harm anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.45,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:13.89,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,That person was never chained.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:18.98,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,You took him to be an obedient dog who could be chained?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:23.29,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee that Bro will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:27.14,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.78,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.45,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,When you failed to finish off Otose too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:36.79,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,When you cut her down so she wouldn't be dragged into this war...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.07,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:43.49,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that there's no point in focusing on Otose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:48.54,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that simple to explain what it is that chains you to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.50,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:53.66,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:58.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to protect her in your stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.26,Main01,Tatsugoro,0000,0000,0000,,Jirocho...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:06.90,Main01,Tatsugoro,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of her... Take care of our town...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:12.17,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are chained to this town by the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:16.18,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,A promise made to a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.25,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,An iron vow of your own choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.59,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,The chains of a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:26.11,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are animals bound by the same chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:27.84,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:35.56,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,One has experienced loss, but accepted the responsibility and continues to protect this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.76,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,The other has experienced loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:44.53,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,but has abandoned the responsibility and chosen to protect this town by using force to conquer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:49.60,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Two beasts whose interests clash, despite sharing the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:53.53,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who will be the last man standing over the Kabuki district?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:57.53,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:15:00.04,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I've already made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:03.78,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be joining you on your rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:08.67,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to help you take over this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:12.68,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,So once this is finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:17.59,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,you'll come back to me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.70,Main01,Jirocho,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.70,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.50,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,With Otose-san's mementos of her husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:36.70,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.19,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said we could do as we please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:41.96,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Take us with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:43.77,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We can help you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:46.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.98,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just here because Gran told me to pick this up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.33,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.73,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of you get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:16:00.45,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,If you shoulder the burden alone and leave us behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:03.44,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to be happy you saved our lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:08.44,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to be happy that Gran saved us if she's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:14.45,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gone, life won't be any fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Life doesn't need to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:23.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.84,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go through that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:32.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:38.68,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be Gintoki Sakata?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:42.60,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,The man who's let so much slip away, who's failed to protect so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.97,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,...but swore that he would never run away from his responsibilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:47.32,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you promise her husband?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:50.49,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've decided to protect something, you'll protect it to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.03,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what makes you Gintoki Sakata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:56.44,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So what if Otose-san's life was in danger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.56,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't enough to kill Otose-san off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:16:59.75,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't enough to kill us off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.38,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't enough to kill you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:04.79,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're going to protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:08.29,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're going to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:12.55,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what Odd Jobs is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:18.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that how the three of us protected so much over the years?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:24.94,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We have not lost anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:29.34,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,So you must not lose your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.94,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine-san, Tama-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:33.07,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gintoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:37.57,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,You have protected us many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.41,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how dire or hopeless the situation was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.72,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.96,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,So it's your turn to trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:49.32,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:53.01,Main01,Catherine,0000,0000,0000,,We can protect Otose-san's home, our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:56.97,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,900)}Kabuki District 1st Street
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:57.65,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the town which brought us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:06.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I bought these for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,but there probably won't be any left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:12.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I'll make another promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:17.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We promise to protect everything which was dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, pops,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:30.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,for leading me to these assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:41.04,Main01,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that group of men or women or both or neither?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:43.46,Main01,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Jirocho's gang and Saigo's people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.35,Main01,K,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's gonna be a war!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.31,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.44,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.19,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mama's the one who's hurting the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:54.65,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs Gin-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:57.11,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Odd Jobs Gin-chan\NSnack Otose
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:19:00.16,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:03.28,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Make a lot of noise for Otose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.99,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.59,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,The store banner is up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.87,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Otose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.61,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:10.22,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This early in the morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.78,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,They work too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:13.34,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,You're missing the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:16.42,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the store banner up when Otose and everyone else is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.13,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.14,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you come back later?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The place is booked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.78,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like drinking by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:31.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Without any interruptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:32.35,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:36.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.79,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.54,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:52.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to keep your stinkin' pig feet out of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.75,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Pako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.18,0:19:56.92,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you would come, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:57.97,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:02.18,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna take on the entire Kabuki District?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.18,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The entire Kabuki District?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:08.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You fools aren't even part of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.89,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're no different from the dogshit on the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:18.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,All I need from the Kabuki District is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.74,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Our Kabuki District...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:22.49,Main01,Tama,0000,0000,0000,,...can be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.45,Main01,Kagura,0000,0000,0000,,...right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Crush us if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:30.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're not letting any of you into our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:31.44,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,Pako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.04,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.58,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.19,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.87,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,It's very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:42.92,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick to have to fight friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:47.60,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I felt relieved when I saw your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.88,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.81,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be right if you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:53.89,Main01,Agomi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:57.88,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Assmi, it would be rude to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.15,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.07,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:07.66,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,Bro and Saigo-san are both protecting what's dear to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:11.18,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:14.66,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Not when you're the one who took what was dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.96,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to apologize. After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.97,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to protect what's dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:27.09,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll steal and destroy what's dear to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:30.38,Main01,Pirako,0000,0000,0000,,...if that's what's needed to take him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:34.76,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,I must pity you, daughter of Jirocho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:40.42,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,The swing of a samurai's blade can silence a thousand words!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.03,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,Warriors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:47.66,Main01,Saigo,0000,0000,0000,,let us hold our conversation in a whirlwind of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:55.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The Otose Family will be paying our respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:58.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, bastards!
